 seat can be reclined back and offers two positions. Adjust it as suited to create the optimal seating position for your child.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_J7U8zB":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"{{ product.metafields.custom.product_sections.value.feature_image_3_bt_rt_.value }}","badge":"","time":"","title":"Premium Safety Guard","text":"<p>The Rito takes every precaution possible to create a safe ride for your child. The safety guard protects them beyond the secure grasp of the 3-point harness seatbelt. Young children can also rest their hands on the safety guard when their arms are not yet long enough to reach the handle bar.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_UMznCd":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"{{ product.metafields.custom.product_sections.value.feature_image_4_bt_rt_.value }}","badge":"","time":"","title":"An Abundance of Storage","text":"<p>Let's face it, you've got a tonne of things to cary around for the comfort and security of your little one. So we've designed 2 bags at different levels of reach for you to store all you need.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_6anEEk":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"{{ product.metafields.custom.product_sections.value.feature_image_5_bt_rt_.value }}","badge":"","time":"","title":"Free Handle & Wheel Clutches","text":"<p>When engaged, the free handle & wheel functions ensures that children do not effect the movement of the trike even when they are pedaling. When the children are old enough to place their feet on the pedals, this function ensures that parents retain control.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_LnUXnj":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"{{ product.metafields.custom.product_sections.value.feature_image_6_bt_rt_.value }}","badge":"","time":"","title":"Folding Footrests","text":"<p>When children have outgrown the footrests, they can be easily folded away with a simple click and release mechanism. Children can comfortably place their feet on the pe